name: PRESTIDIGITATION
description:
You can play in browser and in movil.

Be the fastest in the west, there is no room for both of us in this game!

Be part of this duel in the far west and show your friend who is the fastest. The best of three duels is the owner of the town, don't let your finger fail you!

It's simple just be the first to shoot.

This is part of a mixTape mini games that will be realesed together.
